article_title: No time wasted for TC student
article_text:

og.description: Most college students don’t arrive at school with an entourage.On Monday and Wednesday, Temple College student Arianna Masson of Salado is accompanied by her mother, Staci Masson, and two younger sisters, Annaleisa and Amberlee. She really doesn’t have much choice; Arianna is too young to drive.Arianna, 15, now in her fifth semester at TC, began taking classes there when she was 13.
